,Recommended,249990,16343854,"Posted: 12 June, 2015",all,tl;dr,"Forced is a great ARPG game that features 4 classes. Each class has different unlockable passive and active abilities.  You collect Gems  by completing various tasks within each level and that's how you level up in the game. You play as gladiators (the Storm Bow, the Volcanic Hammer, the Spirit Knives and the Frost Shield) who try to find their freedom and are aided by a spirit called Balfus. Balfus and the fact that you can use him by calling him toward you, lighting torches (and some other things) is the main reason this game stands out as it adds some great and diverse tactics that always serve towards your goal of earning the 3 Gems each level (arena) has to offer. The story is not this game's strong point as the plot is fairly simple. You play as a gladiator that has been FORCED (pun intended) to fight in arenas and Balfus guides you through it and you ultimately have to become a free man.All in all the game is really tactical and has a lot of strategic depth, granted you want to 100% it with friends.The multiplayer is really fun and I recommend you get 3 or 4 friends to play with. The game provides great puzzles and fun combat and with good co-operation it's bound to be a truly fun experience! I thoroughly recommend it!"
