,Recommended,249990,13991324,"Posted: 14 January, 2015",all,dr.doomsday,"Clever and challenging action rpg but best played with 4 friends. Bought the 4 pack during the last steam sale and had a blast going through the levels. Each level is a cleverly designed arena with unique challenges. While difficult to beat the first time, each level also has a time trial and a bonus objective to complete. Beating levels, clearing under a time limit, and completing the bonus objective provides gems which unlock upgrades. Upgrades are unlocked at gem levels, so you can switch between any of the 4 playable characters at any time. Almost all the upgrades are useful and unique, so different players can have very different styles even with the same character.My only complaint about the game is that one of the later levels appears to be bugged in multiplayer and can't be completed."
